{
  "stem": "23410.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- and you-- and nobody had any feeling of death or life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It isn't that oh, yes, it's a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No, they are already over suffering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You spoke about it that you said, how many brothers or sisters did you have?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Four or six or two?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, they are already over, the tragedy, the suffering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am the one that still have to suffer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like a punishment that you are alive, and they are not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember very distinctly where they said, oh, they are already over suffering.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You did not say they died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are already over suffering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Finished.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the father would tell you about his two daughters, the two-- they're beautiful and on, but they are already over their suffering.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were already, like, liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's you that suffers, not them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It should be-- a little bit, I want to tell here a story.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know you should-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about six months ago, I decided-- not six months, six weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I decided maybe I should write about the Kevorkian case, what had really happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I called up my friend, who is the editor of the The is a Jewish agency magazine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his first reaction was, you know, according to Jewish law, it's forbidden to commit suicide, you know, according to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, fine, so forget about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, as such, I don't want even to touch it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, fine, forget about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I am going to write it this week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But next week-- and I [INAUDIBLE] him, but please, do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Read it, and send it right back to me if you don't like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
